Bayes' theorem
========================================================
left: 70%
$$P(A \mid B)= \frac {P(A )P(B \mid A ))}{P(A)}$$   
<br>
$$P(\theta \mid y)= \frac {P(\theta )P(y\mid \theta ))}{P(y)}$$
#### $\theta$ = Model parameter   
#### y = Actual data

***
![bayes](image/Thomas_Bayes.gif)   
*Thomas Bayes (1702 - 1761)*

